<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>浩然文史</strong>
<span>文史类学者、博士团队，让专业的历史更有趣。</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=07fff2d717a8fd26aa7aadb3&lemmaId=8039&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/342ac65c10385343e6388a0f9e13b07eca80882c.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
祭大禹、吃龙眼，酿米酒、喝秋茶，这些白露的民俗，你知道吗？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=07fff2d717a8fd26aa7aadb3&lemmaId=8039&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
白露是农历二十四节气中的第十五个节气，也是秋季的第三个节气。白露是一个与温度有关的节气，白露前后，昼夜温差开始增大，需要注意增加衣物。在民间，白露前后有祭大禹、吃龙眼、酿米酒和饮白露茶等习俗。白露前后多秋燥，饮食方面也要注意清淡。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-09-07</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">442</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="e557d738ab98168063140ab3">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=c2b34a39&authorId=7225f0f4a688293da39a7323&from=lemma" target="_blank">
