<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
你的家乡白露吃什么？我们温州南部是瓯菜十样白
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=e557d738ab98168063140ab3&lemmaId=8039&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">

蒹葭苍苍，白露为霜。所谓伊人，在水一方。溯洄从之，道阻且长。溯游从之，宛在水中央。蒹葭萋萋，白露未晞。所谓伊人，在水之湄。溯洄从之，道阻且跻。溯游从之，宛在水中坻。蒹葭采采，白露未已。所谓伊人，在水之涘。溯洄从之，道阻且右。溯游从之，宛在水中沚。《诗经》里的这首《蒹葭》，...</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-09-07</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">172</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="3e534ed05a0f4546fa5428eb">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=7f91c182&authorId=0c0eaf1e44dbd14fb72e1c20&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/fd039245d688d43f0420e430711ed21b0ff43b62.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>热点说</strong>
<span>时事热点，尽情分享</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=3e534ed05a0f4546fa5428eb&lemmaId=8039&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/a044ad345982b2b7060b82fe3aadcbef76099b70.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
白露，最秋天
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=3e534ed05a0f4546fa5428eb&lemmaId=8039&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
白露是农历二十四节气中的第十五个节气，当太阳到达黄经165度时为白露。2017年9月7日，迎来白露节气。</a>
</p>
